## API Endpoints

### Authentication

- `POST /api/auth/register` вЂ” Register new user
- `POST /api/auth/login` вЂ” Login user

### Tracks

- `POST /api/tracks/upload` вЂ” Upload track
- `GET /api/tracks` вЂ” Get all tracks (with filters)
- `GET /api/tracks/user/my-tracks` вЂ” Get user's tracks
- `DELETE /api/tracks/:id` вЂ” Delete track

### Collaborations

- `POST /api/collaborations/:trackId/request` вЂ” Request collaboration
- `GET /api/collaborations` вЂ” Get user's collaborations

### Submissions

- `POST /api/submissions/:trackId/submit` вЂ” Submit completed version
- `POST /api/submissions/:id/vote` вЂ” Vote on submission

### Messages

- `GET /api/messages/conversations` вЂ” Get conversations
- `POST /api/messages/conversations` вЂ” Start conversation
- `GET /api/messages/conversations/:id/messages` вЂ” Get messages
- `POST /api/messages/conversations/:id/messages` вЂ” Send message

---

## WebSocket Events

```javascript
// Authentication
socket.emit("authenticate", { token });

// Messaging
socket.emit("conversation:join", { conversationId });
socket.emit("message:send", { conversationId, content });
socket.on("message:new", (message) => {});

// Online status
socket.emit("user:online");
socket.on("user:status", ({ userId, online }) => {});

// Typing indicators
socket.emit("user:typing", { conversationId, isTyping });
socket.on("user:typing", ({ userId, isTyping }) => {});
```

